data.title: Pulsar N94J
data.meta_description:
PULSAR_N94J - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. 1) This watch has multiple functions including world time, alarm, and chronograph. It displays 24 time zones and allows the user to select their local time zone. 

2) The modes can be changed by turning the crown, and include time, calendar, world time, alarm setting, and chronograph functions. 

3) To set the time, the user first selects their local time zone in world time mode, then sets the current time and date in time mode. This will automatically set all 24 time zones.
